          <h2 style="font-size:24px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:500;">Israel takes the southern corridor</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;"><strong>Summary: Israel constructed a security corridor that separates Rafah from Gaza.</strong></p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
          Palestinian territory shrunk further as Israel announced the completion of the <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-14-04-2025-h3-6-morag-corridor" target="_blank">Morag corridor</a>. This security corridor separates <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-14-04-2025-h3-7-rafah" target="_blank">Rafah</a> from Gaza as Israel expands its control over 50% of the region. Defense Minister Israel Katz urged the Palestinians to rise against Hamas and demanded the release of remaining hostages. He asserted there would be increased military operations and asked the civilians to evacuate.
        </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">While Hamas is yet to respond, Rafah municipality asserted Israel‚Äôs actions a ‚Äúflagrant breach of international legitimacy.‚Äù Also, there is an <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-14-04-2025-h3-8-ongoing-blockade" target="_blank">ongoing blockade</a> on food, fuel, and humanitarian aid that has affected over 2 million Palestinians. </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">Meanwhile, the Israeli offense persists, with over 21 people killed over 24 hours, raising the toll to 50,000. Israel confirmed that 20,000 of them were militants without providing any evidence. Parallely, the families of the 59 remaining hostages are calling for a ceasefire and an agreement to secure their release. </p>
        </mj-text>
    </mj-section>
